hi, I’ve been M.I.A (typical) 
things are happening in my life, revelations, new beginnings. I’m excited. I can feel myself falling back in love with the things that made me feel the most happy, the most creative. I’m going to get back to being open and vulnerable on my captions/stories/post in general. I’ve closed up big time since I have been on my platforms over the years.. when you are lost, you don’t have the words to share. I didn’t even know of the place I was in until I got here. 
Im happy to be here and to be present. 
I love you guys, I hope you are having a lovely Tuesday 🫶🌎❤️
